org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl

Class MusicArtistImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl.MusicArtistImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.beans.Observable, Artist, MusicArtist
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MusicGroupImpl, SoloMusicArtistImpl

    public abstract class MusicArtistImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements MusicArtist
    Represents an abstract implementation of MusicArtist which let the fields to be get and set and furthermore implements the Observable interface which may help to listen to changes of this entity.
